<plot>Christopher Bee was a respectable member of the hive...until he met Doddsy the Ant! This whimsical, musical adventure takes kids on an exciting ride through a whole new world, where a patch of grass is a mysterious jungle and a tiny pond is an ocean. An imaginative animated tale of love and forgiveness for the whole family to enjoy. Winner of the Film Advisory Board Award of Excellence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?055822</url></doc>
